CIE Automotive Sees Recovery in Europe, Chairman Tells Expansion

-- B y   E m m a   R o s s - T h o m a s
-- 
2011-04-22T07:21:31Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-22/cie-automotive-sees-recovery-in-europe-chairman-tells-expansion.html
CIE Automotive, the Spanish auto
parts maker, expects a recovery in its European market this
year,  Expansion  said, citing an interview with Chairman Anton Pradera.  “This year the positive surprise will be  Europe , where we
will once again earn money at normal levels,” Pradera told the
newspaper. The company aims to pay a dividend as soon as
possible, according to the report.  To contact the reporter on this story:
